Interface TemporalEntity

All Known Subinterfaces:
Address, Person, Phone
All Known Implementing Classes:
AddressEntity, PersonEntity, PhoneEntity
public interface TemporalEntity

Marker interface used to indicate classes and their subclasses that are temporal. All descritpors for classes with this interface will be customized by ConfigureTemporalDescriptors.
